Ok guys i got bored so i started messign with a 508 bulby source. I created a command that writes the npc into npcspawn.cfg.

Here is the code:
[code]					if (cmd[0].equals("npcx")) {
						Engine.fileManager.appendData("npcs/npcspawn.cfg", "spawn	=	"+Integer.parseInt(cmd[1])+"	"+p.absX+"	"+p.absY+"	"+p.heightLevel+"0	0	0	0	0	0	Spawn");
                                                p.frames.sendMessage(p, "<col=0000FF>[Server]Npc spawned at "+p.absX+","+p.absY+".");
					}[/code]

It is very basic as it sets the last 6 integers to 0 automatically, but it works.

